{"tid":1318161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「整理」「集合」疑似冒警恐怖分子襲擊新城市廣場遭市民制服","createTime":"2019-07-15T01:26:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T01:49:48.000Z","uid":79589,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"44a3bd71e17f60c7cf5cf98debe6c1de1b06f333","tid":1318161,"uid":79589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T01:26:53.000Z","msg":"7月14晚，一批懷疑冒充香港警察嘅恐怖分子襲擊沙田新城市廣場，其中一名恐怖分子被一批英勇市民制服。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1FNbVWr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1FNbVWr.png&h=9e345038&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n該批恐怖分子穿戴整套香港防暴裝備，配備防暴盾，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但身上卻沒有任何警員編號、或於當眼位置展示委任証</span></span>。部分恐怖分子更以反光膠紙、反光鏡掩飾身分、阻礙記者傳媒拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EwiFMkV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEwiFMkV.png&h=8783b39b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n恐怖分子於晚上約9時30分突然衝入沙田新城市廣場，恐嚇一般市民。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uksrGUg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuksrGUg.png&h=c4c20d67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有小朋友受驚，需由身邊大人保護。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tupao7C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTupao7C.png&h=c9e1c833&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其中一名恐怖卻意圖攻擊小朋友，令人發指。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/731987203/posts/10156189355552204?s=795165520&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F731987203%2Fposts%2F10156189355552204%3Fs%3D795165520%26sfns%3Dmo&d=MD3su0BfWHBnm8Iidd6ZKQPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=bd8ec960\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/731987203/posts/10156189355552204?s=795165520&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n部分市民逃離商場，但恐怖分子意圖將其趕至高速公路，迫上絕路。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/169166456593130/posts/1258485437661221?s=100004186068871&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F169166456593130%2Fposts%2F1258485437661221%3Fs%3D100004186068871%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=MD3su0BfWHBnm8Iidd6ZKQPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=213894d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/169166456593130/posts/1258485437661221?s=100004186068871&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n有市民不幸遭到恐怖分子脅持、受到不合理的插眼虐待下，以口咬指還擊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/07/14/P8QGYx.gif\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F07%2F14%2FP8QGYx.gif&d=MD3su0BfWHBnm8Iidd6ZKQPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=b2dc69fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://upload.cc/i1/2019/07/14/P8QGYx.gif</a><br />\n另一市民被恐怖分子打暈，仍遭虐待，手腕被其中一名指揮官扭斷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1432983410299343/posts/2338638226400519?s=100001340575038&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1432983410299343%2Fposts%2F2338638226400519%3Fs%3D100001340575038%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=MD3su0BfWHBnm8Iidd6ZKQPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=c846f320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1432983410299343/posts/2338638226400519?s=100001340575038&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n部分市民欲以人道主義，希望救援其中一些傷者卻遭恐怖分子阻撓而。其中一名市民在懷疑有傷者因失救致死而痛哭。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/303668637132303/posts/523716915127473?s=1000124775&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=xmwa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F303668637132303%2Fposts%2F523716915127473%3Fs%3D1000124775%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dxmwa&d=MD3su0BfWHBnm8Iidd6ZKQPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=59969287\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/303668637132303/posts/523716915127473?s=1000124775&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=xmwa</a><br />\n一輪混亂後，一名恐怖分子繼續追打無辜市民。但在落單的情況下，一批英勇市民合力制服該恐怖分子，再移交記者。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/TaipoTaipo/permalink/10162163847700245?sfns=xmwa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2FTaipoTaipo%2Fpermalink%2F10162163847700245%3Fsfns%3Dxmwa&d=MD3su0BfWHBnm8Iidd6ZKQPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=6d1b96b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/TaipoTaipo/permalink/10162163847700245?sfns=xmwa</a><br />\n事件平息後，警察一哥盧偉聰探望部分因對付恐怖分子而受傷警員。有傳媒質疑他放生恐怖分子、不斷推市民、部分警員上前線對抗。現場有市民不滿他的處理方法而問候其娘親表達不滿。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/172Z4YA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F172Z4YA.png&h=5c2dc854&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有警方家屬亦表示一哥不斷推前線上前作為市民及恐怖分子的磨心，一再姑息一班疑似冒警的恐怖分子，感到十分憤怒，意圖發動圍堵一哥住所表達不滿。"},{"pid":"ed816e62267bdece50e9589314f31900692bb47f","tid":1318161,"uid":79589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T01:28:52.000Z","msg":"歡迎補充"},{"pid":"1a44585245c95286491519dadbe7d28e8693dec2","tid":1318161,"uid":125857,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T01:30:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yvjJNc9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyvjJNc9.jpg&h=820b5ca2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kPEhREQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkPEhREQ.jpg&h=6d6e6395&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f4e2dafcab7c6ceb802984ffdfbf4b0ea465b1ff","tid":1318161,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T01:33:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e227e08c88461258f4909159df036fd37e86fad","tid":1318161,"uid":79589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T01:36:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"802aaa7a977426283b652ac12a9bea425321ff67","tid":1318161,"uid":79589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T01:49:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ae1f9614b96a819037736397a13cb2fdd71ac40b","tid":1318161,"uid":253573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T01:49:48.000Z","msg":"推"}]}